  <title>Page Title</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-alpha.6/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-rwoIResjU2yc3z8GV/NPeZWAv56rSmLldC3R/AZzGRnGxQQKnKkoFVhFQhNUwEyJ" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/static/style.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-primary text-white">
  <nav class="navbar navbar-toggleable-md navbar-inverse bg-primary">
    <button class="navbar-toggler navbar-toggler-right" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
      <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
      <img src="/static/logo-h40.png" width="56" height="20">
    </a>

    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
      <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="/team">Home</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="/team">Team</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <main class="container py-md-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-5 offset-lg-1 col-xl-7 offset-xl-0 py-3">
        <h1 class="h1"><mark>Subraya</mark> artículos.</h1>
        <h2>Da solución a las preguntas más&nbsp;relevantes.</h2>
        <p>Liqen es la herramienta que permite extraer datos de artículos con los que quedan respondidas las preguntas de mayor interés periodístico.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 col-xl-4 offset-xl-1">
        <form class="py-3" method="post" action="/login">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Email">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="password">Contraseña</label>
            <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" id="password" placeholder="Contraseña">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-block btn-primary">Entrar</button>
          <p>
            <small>Estamos en fase alpha y solamente se puede acceder a Liqen por invitación.</small>
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <footer class="container small pt-5">
    <ul class="list-unstyled list-inline">
      <li class="list-inline-item">
        <a href="https://github.com/exacs/liqen-core">Github</a>
      </li>
      <li class="list-inline-item">
        <a href="https://exacs.gitbooks.io/liqen/content">API para desarrolladores</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
